<IfModule mod_php5.c>
           php_value post_max_size 200M
           php_value upload_max_filesize 200M
           php_value memory_limit 300M
           php_value max_execution_time 259200
           php_value max_input_time 259200
           php_value session.gc_maxlifetime 1200
       </IfModule>
